Package: timertab
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: manage native systemd timers from a crontab-like YAML config
 timertab manages native systemd timers from a single YAML configuration file.
 It can validate config, reconcile generated service/timer units, inspect
 runtime state, render review bundles for cron migration, and preserve an audit
 trail of config edits through optional git auto-commit support.
